                     <interp inst="t18460202-651-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp> for stealing 2 seals, value 19<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; 1 thimble, 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; 1 handkerchief, 3<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; 27 keys, 7<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; 3 sixpences, and 4 pence; the property of <persName id="t18460202-name-1041" type="victimName">
