                        <interp inst="t18460202-name-1045" type="given" value="WILIAM"></interp>WILIAM MARTIN</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable P</hi> 289.) I apprehended the prisoner at No. 8, New-street, Kent-road—I told him it was for cutting a lady's pocket, and stealing a bunch of keys and other articles.</p>
